speakers:


### Sebastian Neubauer



---
abstract:

AI agents don't just write code — they execute it, deploy it, and act on your behalf. But if agents handle the implementation, does it still matter whether you write Python? This panel, moderated by Sebastian Neubauer, puts the hard questions on the table: what agentic AI means for developers, what we should fear, what we should seize — and whether the language we've built our community around still defines us.
---
full_description:

